OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man found
OL,4,Cdead in house fire
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,7,Fafter a man was found dead following a
OL,8,Fhouse fire in the Vale of Glamorgan.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a property on
OL,11,FMain Street in Barry just after 9am on
OL,12,FSaturday (2 May) following reports of
OL,13,Fthe fire.
OL,15,FFirefighters and paramedics also
OL,16,Fattended but the man was found dead
OL,17,Finside.
OL,19,FHe has not been named, but officers
OL,20,Fsay his family have been informed.
