OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man found
OL,4,Cdead in house fire
OL,6,FA joint investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched between South Wales Police
OL,8,Fand South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService.
OL,11,FMain Street is closed while
OL,12,Finvestigations continue.
